      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, the chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe inspection and VANOS solenoid refresh, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within tight tolerances. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity remains robust, offering a visceral analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
